---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import coverageArea from "../assets/images/coverages.png";
---

<section class="py-24 md:py-32 bg-[#F8FAFC]">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
    <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-16">
      <h2
        class="text-2xl md:text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-[#0F172A] leading-tights mb-6"
      >
        Strategic Fuel Network Across Key Indonesian Corridors
      </h2>
      <div class="w-20 h-[3px] bg-[#018FF5] mx-auto rounded-full mb-6"></div>
      <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
        BAPP maintains strategically positioned distribution points and storage
        assets across key industrial and maritime corridors in Indonesia.
      </p>
      <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
        This geographic positioning enables faster response time, stable bulk
        fuel allocation, and coordinated supply coverage across western,
        central, and eastern regions.
      </p>
      <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
        Distribution and storage points include Sumatra, Kalimantan, Sulawesi,
        Java corridors, and FSU deployment in NTT supporting eastern maritime
        logistics.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- MAP IMAGE -->
    <div class="mb-16">
      <Image
        src={coverageArea}
        alt="Fuel distribution network map showing Sumatra, Java, Kalimantan, Bali and NTT coverage"
        class="w-full h-auto rounded-xl"
      />
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
